# Version bump on code changes

When modifying Book of the End source, installer, or build scripts, increment the patch version (e.g. 2.4.3 ‚Üí 2.4.4) in **all** of these locations:

- `src/BookOfTheEnd/BookOfTheEnd.csproj` ‚Äî `Version`, `FileVersion`, `AssemblyVersion`
- `src/BookOfTheEnd/MainWindow.xaml` ‚Äî title bar `vX.Y.Z` text
- `src/BookOfTheEnd/Views/SettingsWindow.xaml` ‚Äî About version text
- `installer/Package.wxs` ‚Äî `Version="X.Y.Z.0"`
- `installer/Bundle.wxs` ‚Äî `Version="X.Y.Z.0"`
- `build/build-installer.ps1` ‚Äî default `$Version`
- `installer/BookOfTheEnd.Installer.wixproj` ‚Äî `OutputName`
- `installer/BookOfTheEnd.Bundle.wixproj` ‚Äî `OutputName` and `MsiPath`

Use the same version string everywhere. Do not skip the bump for ‚Äúsmall‚Äù changes.
